{"tid":361270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曹操第一謀士係邊個？","createTime":"2017-08-16T03:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T08:59:18.000Z","uid":136553,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64e6457ecc48cc065a88fbe84cafd7b77674d7c4","tid":361270,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"荀彧 荀攸 郭嘉 賈詡 程昱 司馬懿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人覺得係賈詡<br />\n文和亂武<br />\n就係佢煽動李郭挾天子，先出現群雄割據<br />\n可以話，佢製造三國亂世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來又喺宛城害死典韋同曹操大仔<br />\n然後投曹，喺潼關一戰離間韓遂馬超<br />\n最後又擁立曹丕做曹操接班人<br />\n明哲保身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329d015d7412a85d33ab7959b734c7eb6dc1b0ff","tid":361270,"uid":66514,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T03:52:35.000Z","msg":"第一謀士咪係佢自己"},{"pid":"de667732fbd88bb540b618a74e196ea5333f8ac9","tid":361270,"uid":28223,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:16:19.000Z","msg":"郭嘉 <br />\n<br />\n曹操都話有佢係度 赤壁唔會輸 赤壁無打輸既話 咁天下就會係曹操"},{"pid":"a85778341f8d7f75361b96daf9f7686ee3f14f21","tid":361270,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"要看點定義媒士<br />\n綜合咁看  定 只係出謀<br />\n<br />\n第一個<br />\n<br />\n綜合貢獻最大 <br />\n<br />\n呂布起兵差唔多攻下全境 佢死守擋住<br />\n官渡之戰 穩定大後方<br />\n等"},{"pid":"cbb5d9c64943c61bd149c51ffb5a9b7f9061b8a2","tid":361270,"uid":47669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"樓主問曹操謀士<br />\n話係賈詡<br />\n但理據包括整死曹昂同典韋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個人都認為係郭嘉"},{"pid":"8e04dcac04015a4220544b373f1c589d10eb67a3","tid":361270,"uid":1